Source: Al Jazeera's "Global Newly Crowded Pneumonia Report," updated continuously.
”（本文持续更新中。
This article is continuously updated.
文中段首所示时间为本文更新时间。
The time shown at the beginning of the middle paragraph is for this article.
）意大利0800【确诊病例升至1694例，总理签署新疫情防控法令】截至当地时间1日22点，意大利累计确诊病例上升至1694例。
Italy 0800 [confirmed cases rose to 1,694, the Prime Minister signed the new epidemic prevention and control decree as of 22: 00 local time, Italy has a cumulative total of 1,694 confirmed cases.
另死亡41例。
Another 41 cases were killed.
总理孔特签署新疫情防控法令，规定在疫情严重的地区继续暂停集会、体育和其他各类竞赛活动、学校停课至3月8日。
Prime Minister Conte signed a new epidemic prevention and control decree, which provides for the continued suspension of rallies, sports and other forms of competition, and the suspension of schools until 8 March in highly affected areas.
同时重新开放博物馆，和可以提供送至餐桌服务的咖啡馆、餐馆、酒吧。
Museums have also been reopened, as have cafes, restaurants and bars that can provide table service.
多米尼加0800【新冠入侵加勒比海，多米尼加确诊首例】加勒比海岛国多米尼加出现首起确诊病例。
Dominican Republic 0800 [New Crown invasion of the Caribbean Sea, first confirmed case in Dominica]
卫生当局星期天（1日）通报，患者是一名62岁意大利男性游客，他在2月22日抵达多米尼加。
Health authorities reported Sunday that the patient, a 62-year-old Italian male tourist, arrived in the Dominican Republic on February 22.
韩国0800【死亡病例增至22人，“新天地”教主被起诉犯杀人罪】韩国疾病管理本部3月1日晚上发布的最新消息指出，当晚有两名新冠确诊病人死亡，这使该国的死亡病例总计达22人。
Two newly-confirmed cases died that night, bringing the total number of deaths in the country to 22, according to an update released Wednesday night by South Korea's Ministry of Disease Control.
截至1日下午4时，韩国累计确诊3736例。
As of 4: 00 pm on the 1st, the cumulative diagnosis of 3736 cases in Korea.
韩国首尔1日以杀人罪、伤害罪、违反传染病预防管理相关法律为由，向首尔中央地方监察厅起诉新天地教会教主李万熙，以及教会十二支派的支派长。
Seoul, South Korea, 1 on the charges of homicide, injury, violations of laws related to the prevention and management of infectious diseases, Seoul Central District Inspection Office of the Church of Saintiandi, Lee Wanxi, as well as the church 12 faction of the tribal leaders.
首尔方面表示，李万熙等人拒绝病毒检测，并在给政府提交的教徒名单中故意遗漏和隐瞒，阻碍防疫部门工作。
Seoul said Lee and others refused to test the virus and deliberately omitted and concealed it from a list of believers submitted to the government, hampering the work of the epidemic prevention authorities.
这在刑法上属于杀人罪及伤害罪，并涉嫌违反传染病预防法。
This is a crime of homicide and injury in criminal law and is suspected of violating the law on the prevention of infectious diseases.
韩国中央防疫对策本部副本部长权埈郁同时表示，中央防疫对策本部已经通过法务部确认，韩国新天地教会的部分信徒在今年1月曾到访过武汉。
The Ministry of Justice confirmed that some followers of Xintiandi Church of Korea had visited Wuhan in January this year.
美国0800【确诊增长5例，总数增至74例】据美国有线电视新闻网报道，截至当地时间3月1日18时，美国累计新冠肺炎确诊病例74例，较24小时前。
By 1800 hours March 1, 2004, there were 74 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in the United States, up from 24 hours earlier, CNN reported.
其中美国本土确诊病例27例，从日本“钻石公主”号和中国武汉的撤侨人员中分别确诊44例和3例。
Among the 27 confirmed cases in the United States, 44 cases were diagnosed from the Japanese Princess Diamond and 3 cases from the evacuated Chinese people in Wuhan.
新增5例中，1例来自罗德岛州，该患者二月份有意大利旅行史；2例来自华盛顿州；1例来自伊利诺伊州；1例来自加州圣克拉拉县，患者为该县此前一确诊病例的家属。
Of the five new cases, one was from Rhode Island, where the patient had a history of travel in February; two were from Washington State; one was from Illinois; and one was from Santa Clara County, California, and the patient was a family member of an earlier confirmed case in the county.
法国0800【累计确诊病例增至130例，72例为群聚或连锁感染】3月1日晚，法国卫生总局局长萨洛蒙在例行发布会上表示，截至当天16点，法国累计新冠肺炎确诊病例增至130例。
France 0800 cumulative confirmed cases to 130 cases, 72 cases for the cluster or chain infection The total number of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in France as of 16: 00 pm on the night of March 1, said Salomon, director of the French health directorate, said at a regular news conference.
其中12例治愈，2例死亡，116例仍在隔离治疗，9例病情严重。
Of these, 12 cases were cured, 2 cases died, 116 cases are still being treated in isolation and 9 cases are serious.
在这130例确诊病例中，有72例属于法国境内群聚或连锁感染，35例在法国以外的地区感染，23例的感染路径不明。
Of the 130 confirmed cases, 72 cases were clustered or linked in France, 35 cases were infected outside France and 23 cases had an unknown route of infection.
德国0800【累计确诊129例，北莱茵-威斯特法伦州占半数以上】据德国联邦疾控机构罗伯特·科赫研究所3月1日公布的数据，截至3月1日15点，德国已累计确诊新冠肺炎患者129例。
Germany has a cumulative total of 129 confirmed cases, compared with more than half in North Rhine-Westphalia, according to figures released on March 1 by the German Federal Institute for Disease Control and Prevention.
其中北莱茵-威斯特法伦州的确诊病例达74人，超过半数。
Of these, 74 were confirmed in North Rhine-Westphalia, more than half.
英国0800【苏格兰出现首例感染者，英国确诊总数增至36人】3月1日晚，英国苏格兰地区卫生部门宣布，一名近期曾经前往意大利北部旅行的患者被检测确诊感染了新型冠状病毒，成为苏格兰地区首例感染者。
Britain's first confirmed case of coronavirus has been confirmed in Scotland after a recent trip to northern Italy became the first case of the coronavirus in Scotland, authorities said on Monday.
至此英国的四个地区均发现新冠病毒感染者；全境感染人数共计36人。
So far, four parts of the UK have been found to be infected with the virus; the national total is 36.
而3月1日是英国新增确诊病例最多的一天，一共确诊13例。
The highest number of new cases was reported on March 1, when 13 cases were confirmed.
巴林0800【新增6例新型冠状病毒感染者，均有伊朗旅行史】巴林卫生部当地时间1日下午发布公告，确认境内新增6例新型冠状病毒感染者。
Bahrain 0800 [new 6 new cases of coronary virus infection, all have Iran's travel history] Bahrain's Ministry of Health issued a notice on the afternoon of 1 afternoon, confirmed the new 6 cases of new cases of coronary virus infection.
新增感染者中有三名巴林女性公民和和两名巴林男性公民，另有一名沙特公民，均为近期从伊朗经中转达到巴林。
Among those newly infected were three Bahraini women citizens and two Bahraini men, as well as a Saudi citizen, all of whom had recently transited from Iran to Bahrain.
至此巴林境内共计已发现47例新型冠状病毒感染者。
So far, a total of 47 new cases of coronary virus infection have been found in Bahrain.
瑞士0800【确诊病例增至27例，日内瓦病例最多】截至当地时间3月1日晚8时，据瑞士媒体报道，瑞士新冠肺炎病例增至27例。
Switzerland 0800 [confirmed cases increased to 27, the highest number of cases in Geneva] As of 8 p.m. March 1 (local time), Swiss media reported that the number of cases of pneumonia in Switzerland had increased to 27.
其中，日内瓦是瑞士全境确诊病例人数最多的地区，确诊病例为8例。
Of these, Geneva has the highest number of confirmed cases in Switzerland as a whole, with eight confirmed cases.
日内瓦是世界卫生组织和联合国多个专门机构和国际组织总部的所在地。
Geneva hosts the headquarters of the World Health Organization and a number of United Nations specialized agencies and international organizations.
挪威0800【累计确诊19例，无重症患者】当地时间3月1日晚，挪威公共卫生研究所表示，挪威有19例确诊为新冠肺炎，没有感染者患重病。
NORWAY (Reuters) - The Norwegian Institute of Public Health (NIPH) said there were 19 confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia in Norway, with no cases of serious illness.
其中有12例在东部地区，包括乌勒沃医院的5名员工。
Of these, 12 were in the eastern region, including five employees at the hospital in Ulvo.
卑尔根有6例，特罗姆瑟有1例。
There were six cases in Bergen and one in Tromsø.
所有感染者都可以与国外感染者联系起来，除了在挪威感染的19名患者外，还有一名挪威学生在意大利受到感染。
All infected persons can be linked to infected persons abroad, and in addition to the 19 patients infected in Norway, a Norwegian student has been infected in Italy.
伊拉克0800【新增6例确诊病例，均有伊朗旅行史】当地时间3月1日，伊拉克卫生部发布声明称，伊拉克境内新发现6例新冠肺炎确诊病例，其中2例在首都巴格达，4例在北部的苏莱曼尼亚，这些患者在近期均有伊朗旅行史，目前在卫生部下属机构接受治疗与监测。
Iraq 0800 New cases confirmed in Iraq Six new confirmed cases of crowbar pneumonia have been found in Iraq, two in the capital Baghdad and four in Sulaymaniyah in the north, all of whom have a recent Iranian travel history and are being treated and monitored at Ministry of Health facilities.
目前，伊拉克境内感染新冠肺炎的确诊病例总数达到19例。
The total number of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in Iraq now stands at 19.
奥地利0800【累计确诊14例，新增四例】据奥地利卫生部网站及奥地利媒消息，截至当地时间3月1日上午，奥地利共进行了1826次新冠病毒检测，现有确诊病例14例。
Austria 0800 [cumulative confirmed 14 cases, four new cases] As of the morning of March 1, 2006, 1,826 new crown virus tests had been carried out in Austria, with 14 confirmed cases reported, according to the Austrian Ministry of Health website and Austrian media.
1日新增四例确诊病例，均位于维也纳，症状较为轻微。
On the first day, four new cases were confirmed, all located in Vienna, with mild symptoms.
其中两名确诊病例系来自德国的游客，近期曾在德国参加狂欢节活动并接触过一名确诊患者。
Two of the confirmed cases are tourists from Germany who recently attended Carnival in Germany and contacted a confirmed patient.
第三名确诊患者系36岁女性，曾于近期前往意大利米兰。
The third confirmed case is a 36-year-old woman who recently travelled to Milan, Italy.
第四名确诊患者系男性，感染途径暂不详。
The fourth confirmed case was male and the route of infection is unknown.
芬兰0800【累计新冠肺炎确诊病例6例】当地时间3月1日，《赫尔辛基新闻报》报道，芬兰国立卫生和福利研究院以及赫尔辛基和新陆区医院区联合新闻发布会上说，芬兰现已确认有6例新冠肺炎患者。
Finland 0800 Confirmed Cases of New Crown Pneumonia On March 1, Helsinki News reported that Finland had now confirmed six cases of new crown pneumonia at a joint press conference of the Finnish National Institute of Health and Welfare and the Helsinki and New Land hospital districts.
新确诊2例新冠肺炎患者，一个是在校生，另一个是退休人士。
Two new cases of Newly Coronary Pneumonia were diagnosed, one among school students and the other among retirees.
捷克0800【确诊3例病例，有意大利旅行史】当地时间3月2日下午，捷克卫生部长亚当·沃伊捷赫在新闻发布会上称，捷克本土确诊三名新冠肺炎感染病例。
Czech Republic 0800 [confirmed 3 cases, Italy travel history] March 2 afternoon, Czech Health Minister Adam Voitieh said at a press conference, the Czech mainland confirmed three cases of new crown pneumonia.
其中包括两名捷克男性，一名美国女性，所有三人近期都有意大利旅行史。
Among them were two Czech men and one American woman, all of whom had a recent history of Italian travel.
据称，目前三人的病情并不严重。
It is alleged that the three are not currently in serious condition.
西班牙0800【累计确诊74例，周日皇马和巴塞罗那对决】当地时间3月1日下午三点，西班牙新冠肺炎患者确诊人数已达74例。
Spain confirmed 74 cases of pneumonia on Sunday at 3: 00 pm local time (Reuters) - Real Madrid and Barcelona confirmed 74 cases.
排名前三风险的大区为瓦伦西亚15例、马德里14例、安达卢西亚12例。
The top three risk regions were Valencia (15), Madrid (14) and Andalusia (12).
本周日21点整（西班牙时间），西班牙将迎来最受关注的足球比赛，也是世界上最受关注的比赛之一：皇马和巴塞罗那俱乐部之间的对决。
Spain will host one of the world's most watched football matches on Sunday at 21: 00 pm (Spanish time), one of the world's most watched matches: between Real Madrid and Barcelona.
截至目前，政府没有取消比赛的计划。
So far, the government has no plans to cancel the competition.
荷兰0800【新增3例确诊，累计达10例】当地时间3月1日下午，荷兰公共卫生与环境研究院表示，荷兰境内新增3例新冠肺炎确诊病例，其中有1名男性患者，2名女性患者，均居住在不同的城市。
The Netherlands Institute of Public Health and the Environment said Wednesday afternoon that three new cases of pneumonia have been confirmed in the Netherlands, with one man and two women living in different cities.
目前，荷兰卫生部门还不清楚这三名患者被感染的原因和途径。
At present, the Dutch health authorities do not know the cause and way of infection of the three patients.
世卫组织0800【中国境外共58个国家确诊新冠肺炎7169例】据世卫组织每日报告，截至欧洲中部时间3月1日上午10时（北京时间17时），中国（含港澳台）境外共58个国家确诊新冠肺炎7169例，死亡共计104例。
A total of 7169 new cases of pneumonia have been confirmed in 58 countries outside China, with 104 deaths, according to the WHO daily report, reported at 10 a.m. (17: 00 Beijing time) on March 1, Central Europe.
与前一日报告相比，中国外新增新冠肺炎1160例，新增5个国家（阿塞拜疆、厄瓜多尔、爱尔兰、摩纳哥、卡塔尔）出现新冠肺炎病例。
Compared with the previous day's report, 1160 new cases of pneumonia were reported outside China, and 5 new cases (Azerbaijan, Ecuador, Ireland, Monaco and Qatar) were recorded.
